trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeDirective" /> objects.
The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirectiveCollection> class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeDirective> objects.
